ygData.messageBody:
I am at the yahoo group to unsubscribe from this spam list, however,
before I go I'd like to remind you all to keep in mind that not only
are you buying these characters, you are also buying the players
reputation.... Just think a bit before dishing out $400 + on a high
level character - just why do you think they're getting rid of them
in the first place??? Anyone that wants to can find me on the 'non-
spamed' necromancer, cleric or warriors lists....

Kinrea Keres
37th DE Warrior

Sinarya L'achesis
24th DE Necromancer

Zyrrah
7th DE Cleric

Lereny
7th HE Bard

All on Saryrn... Good luck!! =)
